title: [FSX/P3D] Taxi2Gate OTHH Hamad International Airport v1.0
description:
I saw that some users were complaining about the problems in the rips of this airport found here at TPB, so I decided to create this new rip for you.

This rip has been updated with T2G's most recent update for OTHH Hamad International Airport and should work equally well in FSX, P3D v1 and P3D v2.

You can find more information about this rip and installation/uninstallation instructions in the Readme file I prepared.

Enjoy!
